snippet.title: De blob 2 (NDS) Longplay [283]
snippet.description: Played for the first time, this is a decent puzzle platformer. Gets repetitive but not too bad. I get every item in the game too which was nice. Had to do this in two parts and then merge them since I was feeling sick.
